description: Rock A Belly is a premier food truck based out of Phoenix, AZ offering a new take on street food with their brand new food, known as the "Rock-O". Rock A Belly strives to serve perfection with each item on the menu, offering a wide range of Local and Global flavors. Everything is scratch-made with premium local products & never gmo's, by-products or preservatives, offering the best in local and seasonal produce while catering to dietary and vegetarian needs.
name: Rock A Belly
